snippet.title: Run Sausage Run | New Game Trailer | TabTale
snippet.description:
ESCAPE THE KITCHEN! DISCOVER THE GREAT OUTDOORS!
- Run for your life, in a whole new world!
- The danger never stops - even in the park!
- Beware of human legs, killer pelicans and other horrors!

Download the app here: http://bit.ly/RunSausageRunApp

Stop punning and start running! 
Play as the tasty sausage of your choice. Weisswurst or blutwurst, bacon or chocolate… even plumber or cowboy! 

Run through an endless path as you flex that hot-dog body and avoid getting sliced, chopped, burned or smashed! 

Tons of juicy sausages to choose from, tons of hot dog skins. 

Collect coins as you run for your sweet (or spicy) life to buy buns of steel and other cool powerups.


ABOUT US
Crazy Labs is a casual games brand, under which TabTale develops and publishes fun and addictive games. Crazy Labs partners with independent development studios across the globe to create engaging mobile content for audiences of all ages.
